<h2 class="backgrnd12"><span class="text1">AAAI Symposium Papers</span></h2>
<div class="content">

<p>AAAI&rsquo;s Spring and Fall Symposium Series affords participants a smaller, more intimate setting where they can share ideas and learn from each other&rsquo;s research. Topics for the symposia change each year, and the limited seating capacity and relaxed atmosphere allow for workshoplike interaction.</p> 
<p>The <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Symposia/EAAI/eaai-symposia.php">EAAI symposia</a> provide a venue for researchers and educators to discuss pedagogical issues and share resources related to teaching AI and using AI in education across a variety of curricular levels (K-12 through postgraduate training), with a natural emphasis on undergraduate and graduate teaching and learning.</p>
<hr />
<h3>The AAAI Spring Symposium Series </h3>
<p>The Spring Symposium series is typically held during spring break (generally in March) on the west coast. For abstracts and full text of selected Spring Symposium Series papers, you should consult the following:</p>
<ul> 
<li><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php">Spring Symposia Papers</a></li> 
</ul>
<p> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS18">2018</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS17">2017</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS16">2016</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS15">2015</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS14">2014</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS13">2013</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS12">2012</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS11">2011</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS10">2010</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS09">2009</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS08">2008</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS07">2007</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS06">2006</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS05">2005</a> | <br /> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS04">2004</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS03">2003</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS02">2002</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS01">2001</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS00">2000</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS99">1999</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS98">1998</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS97">1997</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS96">1996</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS95">1995</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS94">1994</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS93">1993</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/springsymposia-library.php#SS92">1992</a> |</p>
<hr />

<h3>The AAAI Fall Symposium Series</h3>
<p>The Fall Symposium series is usually held on the east coast during late 
October or early November. For abstracts and full text of selected Spring Symposium Series papers, you should consult the following:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php">Fall Symposia Papers</a></li>
</ul>
<p> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS17">2017</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS16">2016</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS15">2015</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS14">2014</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS13">2013</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS12">2012</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS11">2011</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS10">2010</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS09">2009</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS08">2008</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS07">2007</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS06">2006</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS05">2005</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS04">2004</a> | <br /> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS03">2003</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS02">2002</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS01">2001</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS00">2000</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS99">1999</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS98">1998</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS97">1997</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS96">1996</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS95">1995</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS94">1994</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS93">1993</a> | <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/fallsymposia-library.php#FS92">1992</a> |</p>

<h3>The AAAI Educational Advances in Artificial Intelligence Series</h3>
<p>The EAAI Symposium series is usually held in conjunction with the AAAI Conference on Artificial Intelligence. For abstracts and full text of selected Spring Symposium Series papers, you should consult the following:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/Symposia/eaaisymposia-library.php">EAAI Symposia Papers</a></li>
</ul>
